snippet.title: Dave.EXE: Otherworldly Contracts | Update #5 OUT NOW!!!
snippet.description:
Dave.EXE's Otherworldly Contracts update is out now! Three brand new enemies, a new location that takes place in the Doomy in the Roomy universe, buffs, changes, fixes and more. Come and give Dave.EXE's newest early access build a shot, only on Patreon.


Special thanks to Padre Snowmizzle for making the trailer ► https://twitter.com/PadreSnowmizzle
